# Metric Resource: SequenceMatch
<https://w3id.org/cq4oe/metric/SequenceMatch> a dqv:Metric ;

    dcterms:identifier "https://w3id.org/cq4oe/metric/SequenceMatch" ;
    dcterms:title "Token-level string similarity comparison"@en ;
    rdfs:label "SequenceMatch: Token-level string similarity comparison"^^xsd:string ;
    vivo:abbreviation "sequence_match"^^xsd:string ;
    dcat:version "0.0.1"^^xsd:string ;
    ftr:status "Active"@en ;
    dcat:landingPage <https://w3id.org/cq4oe/metric/SequenceMatch> ;

    # Descriptive Content
    dcterms:description """
This metric computes a token-level similarity between a generated label and each gold-standard label using the longest contiguous matching subsequence (the same algorithm Python's `difflib.SequenceMatcher` uses), returning a score in [0, 1].

**Calculation Process:**

1. Tokenize each label into characters (or sub-tokens after CamelCase split and underscore normalization).
2. Find the longest contiguous matching block, then recursively process the unmatched left and right sides.
3. Return ratio = 2 * matches / (len(generated) + len(gold)).
4. A pair is considered a match if the score is greater than or equal to 0.8 (default lexical threshold).

**Example:**

Generate_Label: WineProducer

Gold_Standard_Label: ProducerOfWine

SequenceMatch(Generate_Label, Gold_Standard_Label) = 0.85

**What is being measured?**

This metric rewards labels that share long contiguous substrings, even when the prefix differs. It is well suited to detecting compound terms reordered or partially renamed.
""" ;
    dcat:keyword "Ontology Concept Matching"@en ;
    dcat:keyword "Metric"@en ;
    dcat:keyword "Classes"@en ;

    # Relationships and Provenance
    dpv:isApplicableFor <https://www.wikidata.org/wiki/Q184754> ;
    ftr:hasBenchmark <https://w3id.org/cq2onto/benchmark/ALL> ;
    sio:SIO_000234 <https://w3id.org/cq4oe/metric/SequenceMatch> ;
    ftr:supportedBy <https://w3id.org/cq2onto/> ;
    dqv:inDimension "Ontology Engineering"^^xsd:string ;

    # Provenance
    dcterms:creator <https://orcid.org/0009-0001-9475-8159> ;
    dcat:contactPoint <https://orcid.org/0009-0001-9475-8159> ;
    dcterms:publisher <https://oeg.fi.upm.es> ;
    dcterms:publisher <https://ror.org/03n6nwv02> ;
    dcterms:license <http://creativecommons.org/licenses/by/4.0/> .

